723
00:46:53.957 --> 00:46:56.892
Citrate de sildénafil,
un inhibiteur de PDE-5

724
00:46:57.060 --> 00:46:59.324
prescrit contre la tension.

725
00:46:59.529 --> 00:47:02.692
